ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702CWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=8b5864b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果十月一我地再幫支共賀一賀佢，搞到全美國都知支共國慶我地用美國國歌慶祝，你話會激到維尼幾咁高興？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實就無話要等到十月一既，<br />\n黎緊每次發夢都可以唱！！！！<br />\n<br />\n但大佬大家真係要練一練佢<br />\n事關首歌音域廣、歌詞繞口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MV with Lyrics: </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702CWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=93c30888\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">Oh, say can you see by the dawn's early light</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">What so proudly we hailed at the twilight's last gleaming?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars through the perilous fight,</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">O'er the ramparts we watched were so gallantly streaming?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare, the bombs bursting in air,</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Gave proof through the night that our flag was still there.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh, say does that star-spangled banner yet wave</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?</span><br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1sKkdk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1sKkdk.gif&h=5c4ce310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, <br />\nthe Revolution of Our Times"},{"pid":"558f77946e06dcfa93119e4e2f6c81b8f85f8d22","tid":1528584,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">3隻眼 6條命 900被捕 無數斷手斷腳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831黨鐵恐襲傷者消息全無</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n九二九三大三罷！<br />\n設死線 升級持續罷工<br />\n日日罷工 日日入機場<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【升級罷工】EndGame＝全面開啟升級抗爭</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">網民問卷調查報告 我們在這沉痛的晚上公佈</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVP4X9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVP4X9g.jpg&h=c7d56cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5iA4Pi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5iA4Pi.jpg&h=b866962b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hL7VVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hL7VVY.jpg&h=fc849ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"288102c1bf8eacc1986bdf972c3a4f09bab5787e","tid":1528584,"uid":3